  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/drcarolinej" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Dr Caroline Johnson</a><span class="ProfileHeaderCard-badges"><a href="/help/verified" class="js-tooltip" target="_blank" title="Verified account" data-placement="right" rel="noopener"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></a></span>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/drcarolinej">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">drcarolinej</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Conservative MP for Sleaford and North Hykeham. I don't respond on twitter please send queries to caroline.johnson.mp@parliament.uk</p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Spring hasnt quite arrived but the Spring Statement is just around the corner. Expect no tax/spend changes until the autumn... heres <a href="/hmtreasury" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="18904582"><s>@</s><b>hmtreasury</b></a> video to explain: <a href="/hashtag/OneFiscalEvent?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>OneFiscalEvent</b></a><a href="https://t.co/QJenXQeo5u" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/hmtreasury/status/968804671048634369" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/hmtreasury/status/968804671048634369"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/hmtreasury/sta</span><span class="invisible">tus/968804671048634369</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Best run of productivity growth since before the financial crisis. 

Employment at a near-record high  and unemployment at a near-record low.

Plus yearly borrowing reduced by over 100bn since 2010.

Good economic news as we build an economy fit for the future.<a href="https://t.co/3lPtPHJk0J" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/3lPtPHJk0J</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">May did something an entire generation of male Conservative politicians has failed to do. She stayed... staying in place and putting her duty to the country before her personal comfort, in 2017 Theresa May exceeded all others <a href="/hashtag/ImWithMay?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>ImWithMay</b></a><a href="https://t.co/UcMqzHBS4h" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2017/12/my-person-of-the-year-theresa-may/" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2017/12/my-person-of-the-year-theresa-may/"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">blogs.spectator.co.uk/2017/12/my-per</span><span class="invisible">son-of-the-year-theresa-may/</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

That's why we have announced that the iconic <a href="/hashtag/bluepassport?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>bluepassport</b></a> will return after we leave the European Union in 2019.<a href="https://t.co/pgQvrBIna5" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://www.conservatives.com/sharethefacts/2017/12/blue-passports" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://www.conservatives.com/sharethefacts/2017/12/blue-passports"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">conservatives.com/sharethefacts/</span><span class="invisible">2017/12/blue-passports</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">The <a href="/hashtag/QuestionTimeNK?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>QuestionTimeNK</b></a> panel is ready for the debate. <a href="/melvynprior" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="316707518"><s>@</s><b>melvynprior</b></a> is hosting with <a href="/MarcJonesLincs" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="732637071647596544"><s>@</s><b>MarcJonesLincs</b></a>, <a href="/drcarolinej" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="797021745563766785"><s>@</s><b>drcarolinej</b></a>, Cllr Lindsey Cawrey and Sarah-Jane Mills from <a href="/NHSLincsWest" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1119631123"><s>@</s><b>NHSLincsWest</b></a> facing the questions.<a href="https://t.co/F17plrXVg9" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/F17plrXVg9</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">It's raining, Mrs C asked me to take the bins out, I said "I'll deal with it". Well done - Hough has gained a brilliant County Councillor<a href="https://t.co/c8wlyMTrKm" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/alex_maughan97/status/860298791890669574" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/alex_maughan97/status/860298791890669574"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/alex_maughan97</span><span class="invisible">/status/860298791890669574</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">A quick break after a busy afternoon of campaigning with <a href="/mattwarman" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="17685009"><s>@</s><b>mattwarman</b></a> and <a href="/RobertJenrick" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2323710210"><s>@</s><b>robertjenrick</b></a>.
